{"tid":1940761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【社福界人士請入】大銀雜誌叫社工捐人工","createTime":"2020-03-24T03:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T14:25:49.000Z","uid":286660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d313552f06b9f0def7ca79fcb89cc90679cdce","tid":1940761,"uid":286660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:37:08.000Z","msg":"自問係長者中心既手足，呢段時間疫情不受控制，雖然中心唔對外開放，但其實每位同工除左每日落區派口罩、搓手液，仲會phone call一班會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有需要既會親自家訪送物資，送飯服務一直無停到。係疫症一爆發個時，我地成班同工周圍R funding班口罩，可以講絕對忙過以前！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啊但原來香港除左林奠條仆街on9之外，大銀雜誌仲on9，叫社工捐人工！<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無錯！係捐人工！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比人圍攻之後，仲怪我地一班前線同工點解將矛頭指向大銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jqqQRNX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjqqQRNX.jpg&h=479bed87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2284946368397433/posts/3139194076305987/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2284946368397433%2Fposts%2F3139194076305987%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1g2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=65edf7aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2284946368397433/posts/3139194076305987/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3月18日仲岀左個Post係度屌長者中心社工唔肯開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大佬啊，其實中心都係按社署要求暫停對外開放，唔代表中心無社工番工嫁！如果疫情係中心爆，你對唔對得住其他會員？區議員派10個口罩有福袋就有哂光環，社工唔通一日派成千個口罩又Po上網拎Halo effect 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQHPnZJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQHPnZJ.jpg&h=67240ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2284946368397433/posts/3141060986119296/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2284946368397433%2Fposts%2F3141060986119296%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1g2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=d1bf701c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2284946368397433/posts/3141060986119296/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不過利申：唔會同區議員割蓆，大家都係為香港人，大銀雜誌唔洗旨意分化我地</strong></span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雜誌編輯：陳曉蕾 懷疑係藍絲，宜家洗哂我班老友記腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b41fde7278acf8fff445cfd2190f6c5898d3ec","tid":1940761,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1g2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=e23bf67e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"9636277151df1730c51f0f50982f760cef358e25","tid":1940761,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:25:49.000Z","msg":"基督教信義會有人確診武漢肺炎 正苦粉飾太平<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949317</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}